n, XD, Mural etc.) Passionate about cryptocurrency industry with interest in building a intuitive complex trading platform for different segments of users. Be aware of current emerging trends in design, product development, crypto and FinTech. Responsibilities: ?? Work with Head of Design on the product flow and wireframe process within projects. Work with product managers and collaborate with engineering teams to turn product ideas into high performing designs. Effectively communicate and collaborate with cross-functional teams to ensure your designs go live and deliver impact. Creating wireframes and layouts. Gathering and evaluating user requirements, in collaboration with product managers and engineers. Illustrating design ideas using storyboards, process flows and sitemaps. Designing graphic user interface elements, like menus, tabs and widgets. Identify and troubleshoot UX problems (e.g. responsiveness). Develop illustrations, logos and other designs using software or by hand. Work with copywriters and creative director to produce final design. ", 
